title: American Horror Story Season 9 TCA Panel Update
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Thank you so much for immediately telling us and not dragging it out for nothing. Much respect.
Man I always miss the live stream. It’s my fault I fell asleep super early last night. Love this though and love you Mary it’s always good to see you.

That's unfortunate but it makes me more curious about season 9. I have never seen Scream Queens, is it that good? More AHS seasons yes!!!! But I hope it stays on FX passed season 10. Please please please!
